9:00:00.000Z"],[18,19,20],"pregnancy","wellness","fitness",false,"/images/mama-1.png","Exercise during pregnancy offers numerous benefits for both mother and baby.\n\n![Mama Motion](/images/mama-1.png)\n\n## First Trimester\nMaintain pre-pregnancy fitness with walking, swimming, and light yoga.\n\n## Second Trimester\nContinue with modified movements as your body changes.\n\n## Third Trimester\nFocus on gentle movement and preparation for labor.\n\nAlways consult your healthcare provider before starting any exercise program.\n\n![Mama Motion](/images/mama-2.png)","src/content/blog/safe-exercises-pregnancy.md","4ba52fa1682eeb22",{"html":27,"metadata":28},"\u003Cp>Exercise during pregnancy offers numerous benefits for both mother and baby.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"/images/mama-1.png\" alt=\"Mama Motion\">\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"first-trimester\">First Trimester\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Maintain pre-pregnancy fitness with walking, swimming, and light yoga.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"second-trimester\">Second Trimester\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Continue with modified movements as your body changes.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"third-trimester\">Third Trimester\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Focus on gentle movement and preparation for labor.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Always consult your healthcare provider before starting any exercise program.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"/images/mama-2.png\" alt=\"Mama Motion\">\u003C/p>",{"headings":29,"localImagePaths":40,"remoteImagePaths":41,"frontmatter":42,"imagePaths":45},[30,34,37],{"depth":31,"slug":32,"text":33},2,"first-trimester","First Trimester",{"depth":31,"slug":35,"text":36},"second-trimester","Second Trimester",{"depth":31,"slug":38,"text":39},"third-trimester","Third Trimester",[],[],{"title":14,"description":15,"pubDate":43,"tags":44,"draft":21,"image":22},["Date","2026-07-08T09:00:00.000Z"],[18,19,20],[]]